sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant VB as Visitor Browser
  participant W as Embedded widget.js
  participant API as Next.js API
  participant DB as Supabase DB
  participant GEO as ipapi.co

  VB->>W: Load page with widget script
  W->>W: Extract widgetId from script URL
  W->>API: POST /api/track (widgetId, pageUrl, referrer)
  API->>DB: Validate widgetId + user paid status
  API->>DB: Check monthly_pageviews limit
  API->>GEO: GeoIP lookup (with timeout)
  GEO-->>API: Location or fallback Unknown
  API->>DB: Insert visitors row
  API->>DB: RPC increment_monthly_pageviews
  API-->>W: 200 Tracked

  W->>API: Open SSE /api/visitors/:widgetId/stream
  loop Every few seconds
    API->>DB: Query latest visitors + counts
    API-->>W: Snapshot only if changed (hash dedupe)
  end

  alt SSE unavailable / error
    loop Every 10s
      W->>API: GET /api/visitors/:widgetId?limit=N
      API->>DB: Query visitors + totalToday + activeNow
      API-->>W: JSON payload
    end
  end

  W->>VB: Render/update globe points and rings
